:"recCIAJIz0iVd4ZTe","target":"recdMHFSmu222VnJG","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recCIAJIz0iVd4ZTe","target":"recUn6eVJDoG4xI0j","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recCIAJIz0iVd4ZTe","target":"recDsLjW4riPOxvp4","label":"mentions"}],"verses":[{"id":"recnPzSRXI8CPh4bz","ref":"Num.31.1","text":"And the LORD spake unto Moses, saying,","year":-1452},{"id":"reciMm8xsCmhVVU5q","ref":"Num.31.2","text":"Avenge the children of Israel of the Midianites: afterward shalt thou be gathered unto thy people.","year":-1452},{"id":"recr0bhALWhV0jtUi","ref":"Num.31.3","text":"And Moses spake unto the people, saying, Arm some of yourselves unto the war, and let them go against the Midianites, and avenge the LORD of Midian.","year":-1452},{"id":"recm3BdnFAaRU2n2X","ref":"Num.31.4","text":"Of every tribe a thousand, throughout all the tribes of Israel, shall ye send to the war.","year":-1452},{"id":"recFfd38bsyEa56rs","ref":"Num.31.5","text":"So there were delivered out of the thousands of Israel, a thousand of every tribe, twelve thousand armed for war.","year":-1452},{"id":"rec47FklTJ0ZuD2TY","ref":"Num.31.6","text":"And Moses sent them to the war, a thousand of every tribe, them and Phinehas the son of Eleazar the priest, to the war, with the holy instruments, and the trumpets to blow in his hand.","year":-1452},{"id":"recxITOetdFqGJD8s","ref":"Num.31.7","text":"And they warred against the Midianites, as the LORD commanded Moses; and they slew all the males.","year":-1452},{"id":"rect4qbeinkzSwR4A","ref":"Num.31.8","text":"And they slew the kings of Midian, beside the rest of them that were slain; namely, Evi, and Rekem, and Zur, and Hur, and Reba, five kings of Midian: Balaam also the son of Beor they slew with the sword.","year":-1452}]}
